# Database Design

## Tables

### sources

Stores configured news sources.

Columns:

| Name | Type |
|--------|--------|
| guid | UUID |
| url | TEXT |
| created_at | TIMESTAMP |

---

### news_chunks

Stores searchable content.

Columns:

| Name | Type |
|--------|--------|
| guid | UUID |
| source_guid | UUID |
| text | TEXT |
| embedding | VECTOR |
| created_at | TIMESTAMP |

---

## Chunk Rules

Each chunk contains only:

- text
- creation date

No metadata storage:

- title
- author
- category
- tags
- image
- article url

must not be stored.

---

## Indexes

Required:

```sql
ivfflat
```

Vector index:

```sql
CREATE INDEX news_chunks_embedding_idx
ON news_chunks
USING ivfflat (embedding vector_cosine_ops);
```

---

## Migrations

All schema changes must use Alembic.

Direct schema modifications are forbidden.